{"THEIFORM":[{"def":"Having the form of tea.","pos":""}],"THEIR":[{"def":"The possessive case of the personal pronoun they; as, their houses; their country.","pos":""}],"THEISM":[{"def":"The belief or acknowledgment of the existence of a God, as opposed to atheism, pantheism, or polytheism.","pos":""}],"THEIST":[{"def":"One who believes in the existence of a God; especially, one who believes in a personal God; -- opposed to atheist.","pos":""},{"def":"Of or pertaining to theism, or a theist; according to the doctrine of theists.","pos":""}]}